title: Backflip Animation Pack
longDescription:
These animations are for 4.27/5.0/5.1 version, for default skeleton (SK_Mannequin).

Preview: https://youtu.be/An2TOYoDOeY

Contains:

52 Backflip Animations Files:

  • 26 animations (In-Place)
  • 26 animations (With Root Motion)

The Backflip Variations: (In-Place + Root Motion)

  1. Backflip
  2. Backflip Under Tuck
  3. Backflip Pistol
  4. Backflip Pike
  5. Backflip Split
  6. Backflip Layout
  7. Backflip Layout OneAirStep (Left + Right)
  8. Backflip Layout AirWalk (Left + Right)
  9. Backflip OneLeg (Left + Right)
  10. Backflip OneLeg Layout (Left + Right)
  11. Backflip OneLeg Layout AirWalk (Left + Right)
  12. Backflip Russian
  13. Backflip Russian Layout
  14. Backflip Russian Layout AirWalk (Left + Right)
  15. Backflip OneLeg Russian (Left + Right)
  16. Backflip OneLeg Russian Layout (Left + Right)
  17. Backflip OneLeg Russian Layout AirWalk (Left + Right)

Other:

These are for starters, over time I will add more variants.
